body_html:
We don't have immediate plans to add a CycleGAN estimator, but we're going to add a StarGAN estimator within the week.

It should be straightforward to extend CycleGAN to CycleGANEstimator by following how GANEstimator is made; feel free to send me a pull request and I'll approve it.
